Class FlurryPerformance

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.flurry.android.FlurryPerformance

  • public class FlurryPerformance
extends java.lang.Object
    The Flurry Performance metrics allow you to measure and understand how your app performs on the range of devices.

    • Method Detail

      • reportFullyDrawn

        public static void reportFullyDrawn()
        Report to the Flurry Cold Start metrics that your app is now fully drawn. This is only used to help measuring application launch times, so that the app can report when it is fully in a usable state similar to android.app.Activity#reportFullyDrawn.
